  <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">What Is See Guru?</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">See Guru is an online tutor marketplace that connects English learners with native and near-native speakers for 1-on-1 video lessons. The platform was founded to make language learning more accessible, with a strong focus on affordability and flexible scheduling.</p>
  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Unlike platforms that require monthly subscriptions, See Guru operates on a pay-per-lesson basis. Learners browse tutor profiles, read reviews, and book individual lessons whenever it suits them. This makes it one of the most flexible options available for casual or budget-conscious learners.</p>
  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">The platform is particularly popular with learners seeking tutors from the Philippines, Indonesia, and other Southeast Asian countries, where English is widely spoken and tutors can offer competitive rates.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">How Does See Guru Work?</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Getting started on See Guru is straightforward. You create a free account, browse the tutor directory, and book a lesson with your chosen tutor. Lessons take place on See Guru's built-in video platform, so you do not need to install any special software.</p>

  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-neutral-300">Here is the basic process:</strong></p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-neutral-400 mb-6">
    <li><strong class="text-neutral-300">Create an account:</strong> Sign up with your email or Google account. No payment information is required to browse.</li>
    <li><strong class="text-neutral-300">Browse tutors:</strong> Filter by language, specialty, price, rating, and availability. Each tutor profile shows their experience, teaching style, and student reviews.</li>
    <li><strong class="text-neutral-300">Book a lesson:</strong> Choose a time slot that works for you and pay with credits. Trial lessons are often available at a discounted rate.</li>
    <li><strong class="text-neutral-300">Attend your lesson:</strong> Join via the See Guru website or mobile app. Most tutors use their own lesson materials.</li>
    <li><strong class="text-neutral-300">Track progress:</strong> After each lesson, you can rate your tutor and leave feedback to help other learners.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">Pricing</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">See Guru's pricing is one of its strongest selling points. Tutors set their own rates, and the platform shows a wide range of options to fit nearly any budget.</p>

